I turn 19 tomorrow and it was your memorial tribute yesterday, We had plans for our 21st together but ig god’s plan was something else. 
I very honestly don’t know how to cope with this or what to even react. 
I could spend hours writing things here but I just wouldn’t do that, instead I’ll just say Thankyou for always being my best friend adi, staying up all night long making sure i don’t feel alone or drained, you kept telling me stay detached from everyone and accept that everything is temporary but i never would’ve imagined one day you wouldn’t be here. 
No matter how huge my mess up ever was, you always forgave me. You always knew what logic to put behind things and you made me promise whatever backfires i wouldn’t let it affect me. 
So ig it’s my turn to forgive you for this? Guess I’ll have to deal with all of it on my own now 
I really wish sometimes you weren’t so good at all with these impromptu decisions, some things are better thought through. 

Boyfriends and Girlfriends come and go, this is for life. I’d rather live with the pain than to accept that you’re not gonna be here. 
My only right decision 💎 🦕💙

No one could ever be Aditya Verma.
You were my mom’s favourite child for a reason ❤️
